Class MtBatchBinarySmsResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.clxcommunications.xms.api.MtBatchSmsResult
      • com.clxcommunications.xms.api.MtBatchBinarySmsResult

  • @Value.Immutable
public abstract class MtBatchBinarySmsResult
extends MtBatchSmsResult
    Objects of this class contain information about a binary SMS batch. The information includes the binary body, the batch identifier, the creation time, and so on.
